dooyit.ui

Class UICategoryBoxContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • dooyit.ui.UICategoryBoxContainer

  • public class UICategoryBoxContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    The UICategoryBoxContainer class contains the methods to create and retrieve a list of UICategoryBox objects. It also has a container view which contains the category menu buttons for the list.
    Since:
    2016-04-10
    Version:
    0.5
    Author:
    Wu Wenqi
